{
  "page": "Against the Unnatural",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Against the Unnatural</b></i> is a book written by <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vanyon\" title=\"Vanyon\">Vanyon</a>. It contains certain proofs of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragons\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragons\">dragons</a> having existed in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> even in the earliest of days, before <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a>'s rise to power. The work disputes <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Barth\" title=\"Barth\">Barth</a>'s speculation in his <i><a href=\"/index.php/Unnatural_History\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Unnatural History\">Unnatural History</a></i> that Valyrian <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodmage\" title=\"Bloodmage\">bloodmages</a> experimented with <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">unnatural arts</a> to create dragons from <a href=\"/index.php/Wyvern\" title=\"Wyvern\">wyverns</a>, as Vanyon, like most maesters, considered Barth's claim to be far-fetched.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf834_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf834-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Against_the_Unnatural&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf834-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf834_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; Beyond the Free Cities&#32;(Sothoryos).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404043147\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.038 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 115/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8575/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 597/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 28/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 426/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   33.763      1 -total\n 81.85%   27.636      1 Template:Italic_title\n 13.69%    4.623      1 Template:Ref\n  9.02%    3.046      1 Template:Ref/core\n  3.78%    1.276      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:20114-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404043147 and revision id 322865\n -->\n",
